# Verion 0.7.0_pre-alpha

This update focuses on **progression, rewards, shop systems, premium content, UI polish, and significantly improved ball physics**.

---

## 🎁 NEW: Player Progression & Reward System

### 🆙 Level-Up Rewards

* Players now earn **rewards when leveling up**
* Milestone levels can grant **random cosmetic rewards**
* Rewards are clearly displayed on a redesigned end screen

### 🎉 New Reward Reveal Screen

* Brand-new **reward reveal animations** at the end of matches
* Items now display:

  * Rarity color backgrounds
  * Rarity badges
  * Improved title rendering
  * Cleaner animations and transitions

### 🎲 Random Item Drops

* Random rewards now use a **weighted rarity system**
* Certain items are excluded from random drops to preserve rarity

### 💰 Starting Economy Update

* New players now start with **500 Cash**
* Economy and item ownership logic improved for reliability

---

## 🛒 Shop & Premium Store Overhaul

### 🏪 Daily Rotating Shop

* Shop rotates items daily using improved calculation logic
* Weighted rarity system for fair rotation
* Ownership validation improved to prevent duplicate purchases

### 💎 Premium Store Added

* New **Premium Store** for game passes and developer products
* Improved item previews with character model display
* Better hover effects and ownership indicators
* Cleaner confirmation dialogs with preview support

### 🪙 Developer Product Support

* Developer product purchases now:

  * Process correctly
  * Grant coins instantly
  * Validate securely server-side

---

## 👕 Customisation & Character Improvements

### 🔢 Kit Number System

* Players can now set their **Kit Number**
* Includes increment/decrement UI and confirmation system
* Fully customizable

### 🎭 Celebration Previews

* Celebrations can now be previewed in-menu
* Improved visibility handling during cinematics
* Character properly restores after preview

### 🧢 Accessory Cleanup

* Non-essential accessories removed on spawn for cleaner visuals and performance

### 🎨 Item Visual Enhancements

* Rarity-based background colors
* Particle indicators with tooltips
* Improved kit text rendering and cleanup

---

## 🎮 Controller & Input Improvements

* Improved **gamepad support**

  * D-Pad tool switching
  * Proper PlayStation & Xbox input prompts
  * Cleaner tool activation handling
* Refined set piece action bindings
* Free kick and penalty prompts now display correctly

---

## ⚽ Major Ball Physics Upgrade

### 🌀 Magnus & Spin Physics

* Added **Magnus force** for realistic curved shots
* Added drag forces
* Implemented spin decay for natural ball behavior
* Trajectory prediction now matches live physics

### 🔧 Shot Tuning

* Increased maximum shot power
* Adjusted gravity scaling for low-angle shots
* Reduced excessive spin for better balance
* Improved ball rotation syncing

### 🧠 Smarter Foul Logic

* Advantage and foul awarding now better account for ball ownership

